{"title": "Putin sending medical supplies to help U.S. fight coronavirus: IFX", "link": "https://news.yahoo.com/putin-sending-medical-supplies-help-194724120.html", "description": "<p><a href=\"https://news.yahoo.com/putin-sending-medical-supplies-help-194724120.html\"><img src=\"http://l.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ANR_PdwWiywcD4mnQWMdZA--/YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b247aD04Njt3PTEzMDs-/https://media.zenfs.com/en-US/reuters.com/6c955adee1f372f3143977df25402f0f\" width=\"130\" height=\"86\" alt=\"Putin sending medical supplies to help U.S. fight coronavirus: IFX\" align=\"left\" title=\"Putin sending medical supplies to help U.S. fight coronavirus: IFX\" border=\"0\" ></a>Russia is sending the United States medical equipment to help fight the coronavirus outbreak, the Interfax news agency reported on Tuesday, citing the Kremlin spokesman Dmitry Peskov.  President Vladimir Putin made the proposal in a phone conversation with President Donald Trump on Monday, when they discussed the coronavirus and oil markets, directing their energy ministers to speak.  \"Trump gratefully accepted this humanitarian aid,\" Interfax quoted Peskov as saying.<p><br clear=\"all\">", "date": "Tue, 31 Mar 2020 15:47:24 -0400", "categories": ["Yahoo News - Latest News & Headlines"], "source": ["Yahoo News - Latest News & Headlines"]}
